      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained, making it a reliable choice for any driver. The engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts as it should, providing a confident driving experience. While there are some minor cosmetic imperfections and light wear on the interior consistent with regular use, the car is structurally sound and mechanically dependable. You can expect a solid, road-ready vehicle that requires no immediate major repairs.",
